WEBVTT

00:09:58.610 --> 00:10:00.739
protected behind its Great Wall.

00:10:00.763 --> 00:10:02.281
But think twice.

00:10:02.305 --> 00:10:04.351
The Chinese official ideology?

00:10:04.375 --> 00:10:07.122
Marxism, made in Germany.

00:10:08.064 --> 00:10:09.709
One of China's biggest religions?

00:10:09.733 --> 00:10:12.341
Buddhism, imported from India.

00:10:12.365 --> 00:10:14.650
India's favorite pastime?

00:10:14.674 --> 00:10:15.890
Cricket.

00:10:16.222 --> 00:10:18.640
I really love this quote from Ashis Nandy,

00:10:18.664 --> 00:10:23.541
who said, "Cricket is an Indian game
accidentally discovered by the British."

00:10:23.565 --> 00:10:25.123
(Laughter)

00:10:25.147 --> 00:10:31.692
So these are good reminders that a lot
of what we love in our national traditions